        <num>51-6-1</num>
        <content>
          <p>Fraud, accompanied by damage to the party defrauded, always gives a right of action to the injured party.</p>
          <p>(Orig. Code 1863, § 2900; Code 1868, § 2906; Code 1873, § 2957; Code 1882, § 2957; Civil Code 1895, § 3813; Civil Code 1910, § 4409; Code 1933, § 105-301.)</p>
